Wolfram Research Logo Wolfram Research is an American multinational company that creates computational technology. Wolfram’s flagship product is the technical computing program Wolfram Mathematica, first released on June 23, 1988. Other products include Wolfram Alpha, Wolfram SystemModeler, Wolfram Workbench, gridMathematica, Wolfram Finance Platform, webMathematica, the Wolfram Development Platform, and the Wolfram Programming Lab. Wolfram Research founder Stephen Wolfram is the CEO. The company is headquartered in Champaign, Illinois, United States. Source
